285
00:17:48,230 --> 00:17:49,190
Morning,

286
00:17:49,950 --> 00:17:50,680
Nianchu.

287
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,560
Morning, Guozhi.

288
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:52,830
Here's your breakfast.

289
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:55,190
