314
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:58,230
Ex-boyfriend. We don't have relationship now.

315
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:03,680
Everyone, this is Mr. Li of the Yuntai Cooperation.

316
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:05,470
